{"tid":370723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門颱風期間3死　男子遭強風吹倒撞牆亡","createTime":"2017-08-23T07:39:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T10:35:50.000Z","uid":20933,"like":92,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"96b66457bf42110dbcdf09ab7829b35272cbfe0c","tid":370723,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:39:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170823/s00001/8b1e917afff063eb523352615895aadf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170823%2Fs00001%2F8b1e917afff063eb523352615895aadf.jpg&h=53d7a058&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「天鴿」來襲，澳門廣泛地區受波及，出現停電、水浸。澳門當局指颱風期間，有3人死亡，其中一名30歲男子遭強風吹倒撞牆，送院經搶救後均證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n該名30歲男子持藍咭，即在澳門工作的外地人須申請的外僱身份認別證。另外兩名死者分別為一名62歲從高處墮下的澳門男居民，以及一名遭重型車輛輾過的45歲內地男遊客。<br />\n<br />\n另外，今早於筷子基雅典灣附近，有4人一度失蹤，其中2人獲救，2人仍未尋回，中午時分，內港一艘本澳停泊漁船沉沒，澳門當局正在跟進中。"},{"pid":"136a8025ec6405f1fa8edee503c523075e3c7b7c","tid":370723,"uid":12021,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:40:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"add4afc6d5539ac59bab1556b1b7acc943acef34","tid":370723,"uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T08:06:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f947ddeb88a50bd374493fa887ad4f66aaa5f1b","tid":370723,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T08:30:40.000Z","msg":"慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"092dc0f1f9b2bb8375ac0424a76e013b47efb576","tid":370723,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T08:33:14.000Z","msg":"睇黎又係大陸人"},{"pid":"309e923138476b432bc5ae62a502faeb68076010","tid":370723,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T08:34:01.000Z","msg":"畀貨車壓死果個係&hellip;"},{"pid":"132b6d89300d4061565bd993fcb6ac9ed6efc9c4","tid":370723,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB